      "writtenOn": "2021-04-02T04:57:04Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We got the error because writer still tries to write when reader closed, right.\n\nAnd in this CL I make sure writer closes before reader, so we should only see \"subsequent reads from the read half of the pipe will return no bytes and EOF.\"",
