      "writtenOn": "2021-04-02T05:44:26Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We read from rbe-cas and write the chunks to pipe, then bqexporter read from the pipe.\n\nSo the situation I\u0027m imagine is that:\n1. we finished erading from rbe-cas -\u003e close pw -\u003e close pr.\n2. bq_exporter reads contents from pipe.",
      "parentUuid": "1297e878_61ec336e",
      "revId": "df0f0fbddf75290ae022042e3f65a720f23991c5",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba"
